<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, November 30 (Xinhua) -- Bahrain and Russia
initialed today a trade cooperation agreement in the Bahraini
capital Manama in a bid to boost bilateral economic ties, the
Bahraini News Agency monitored here reported.
</P>
