it to win the gold medal at the Atlanta Olympics. He later quit
for poor treatment, and took charge of Qatar's national team
before poor results cost him the job.
</P>
<P>
Mezsoly failed in his bid for the post in March before
Troussier was appointed.
</P>
<P>
Along with Morocco, South Africa, Cameroon and Tunisia, Nigeria
has secured one of the five berths from the African qualifying
tournament for the World Cup finals in France next year. 
