status has gotten better with each passing year, but they still
face many problems in the 1990s, such as unemployment and poverty.
</P>
<P>
Hu went on say that the women's federation should do three
things: First, arouse women to get them involved in a high-profile
program developing agriculture by using science and technology;
second, help unemployed female workers find new jobs; and third,
promote good morale in families.
</P>
