<HEADLINE> S. Africa to Host International Leather Show </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, December 1 (Xinhua) -- An international leather
exhibition will open Wednesday in Midrand, a city between
Johannesburg and Pretoria, local daily Business Day reported
today.
</P>
<P>
The three-day show is an exhibition of products and forum for
the cooperation and exchange of technology with 28 countries and
regions taking part, organizers said.
