during the August-October period dropped to 3.0 percent, latest
statistics show.
</P>
<P>
Figures released by the Macao Census and Statistics Department
show that the jobless rate declined 0.1 percent from the
July-September period this year.
</P>
<P>
It also represented a drop of 1.4 percent from the
August-October period last year.
</P>
<P>
The rate of underemployment reached 1.1 percent, down 0.1
percent from the July-September period. But it rose 0.3 percent
from the same August-October period last year.
</P>
<P>
The rate of unemployment reached as high as 4.8 percent last
year, but it has declined since late last year. 
