at 102.6 in Shanghai, China's largest industrial city, last
October, 1.7 percentage points lower than that in September.
</P>
<P>
A survey of 253 commodities conducted by the Shanghai Price
Bureau showed an increase in the prices for 56 commodities and a
drop in the prices for 90 other commodities in October.
</P>
<P>
