<HEADLINE> New Port City Emerges in Southeast China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, December 1 (Xinhua) -- Longhai, a new port city, is
thriving in Zhangzhou, southeast China's Fujian Province.
</P>
<P>
