<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG -- The Presidium of the Conference for Electing
Deputies of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region to the
Ninth National People's Congress of China made public the list of
candidates here Monday.
</P>
<P>
The 72 candidates each obtained nomination by at least 10
members of the 424-strong Election Conference from November 13 to
28. According to the Election Method, as the number of nominees
exceeds the number to be elected (36) by more than one-half, a
preliminary election will be held on the morning of December 6 to
determine the 54 official candidates on the merit of votes. The
final election is scheduled for December 8. (Hong Kong-Candidates
Announced)
