<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, November 30 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
had an informal meeting with German Federal Chancellor Helmut Kohl
Sunday at the president's residence in Moscow suburb.
</P>
<P>
The President's press office said the two leaders exchanged
views on bilateral relations and some international issues.
</P>
<P>
Press reports here said Yeltsin and Kohl discussed in detail
the schedule of their meetings next year, first in Bonn in spring
